New Covenant Prophetic and Miracle Temple (a.k.a Temple of Covenant) Quarry Bioku, Iyana Agbala- Olode, Ibadan, will hold its Founders’ Day, thanksgiving and ordination services on Sunday. Minister in charge Prophetess Olabamiji Omotayo said the theme of the programme is ‘Praise the Lord’, while the speaker of the day is Prophet Oladele Oladepo.